Dormehl said paramedics found the man had been ejected from the Ford Fiesta as the vehicle rolled down an embankment. "The man was found under the car and paramedics found epileptic medication next to the car." "It is also believed that the man could have had an epileptic seizure while driving and that this could have caused him to lose control of the vehicle," said Dormehl. Local authorities are investigating. African News Agency